node.text:
#FlashBackFriday, circa 1988. 
This was the first car I ever drove, a #Peugeot 504, and the automobile I learned to drive a manual with.
The license plate: IM7373AD...I will never forget her!
#naija

node.text:
Met amazing new people.
Had a blast.
Combined science and entertainment.
Yesterday, the 2 episode premiere of #MotorMythbusters launched in the @MotorTrendApp 
I hope you enjoyed the mayhem... with many more episodes to come!
.
It was an honour co-hosting with @torybelleci and @pistonsandpixiedust
